msgid "Iti kho, ambaṭṭha, yadā khattiyo paramanihīnataṃ patto hoti, tadāpi khattiyāva seṭṭhā, hīnā brāhmaṇā. "
msgstr "Yet still the aristocrats are superior and the brahmins inferior. "

